          "text": "At process termination"
        },
        {
          "key": "D",
          "text": "During context switching"
        }
      ],
      "correctAnswer": 1,
      "explanation": "Copying happens only when a process tries to write to a shared page, triggering a page fault.",
      "difficulty": "medium"
    },
    {
